race.comment: ALL JAZZ (4) made light work of the tricky draw with a strong early sectional but swamped late when a close up fifth (29.03) at this track over 510m. Form from her last run is proving strong. Bold showing expected. BIG YETI (8) put a gap on his rivals last start. Must be respected. PAW FREDRICK (5) hasn't been far from the placegetters of late, beaten 4.3 lengths at Geelong last start. Can make an impact in this line-up. AKINA JACK (6) has been ticking along well with a string of top-four finishes, clocking in second in the last two outings. Can be competitive again.
